    CollectionExp, EnumLiteralExp, IfExp, LetExp, MapExp, OclType, OclUndefinedExp, PrimitiveExp, PropertyCallExp, SuperExp, TupleExp, VariableExp
    public abstract class OclExpression
extends LocatedElement
    A representation of the model object 'Ocl Expression'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Type
    • If Exp3
    • Applied Property
    • Collection
    • Let Exp
    • Loop Exp
    • Parent Operation
    • Initialized Variable
    • If Exp2
    • Owning Operation
    • If Exp1
    • Owning Attribute
    See Also:
    OCLPackage.getOclExpression()
